00:11:30.273 --> 00:11:32.441
NOĆNOG PUZAČA!

00:11:52.212 --> 00:11:52.961
Oprez...

00:11:53.129 --> 00:11:54.630
Visoki napon!

00:11:54.839 --> 00:11:56.965
<i>Žao mi je, mutanti!</i>

