00:17:02.772 --> 00:17:05.107
KSAVIJEROVA ŠKOLA
ZA NADARENU DECU

00:17:05.274 --> 00:17:06.942
<i>Miriše na staro unutra.</i>

00:17:07.110 --> 00:17:08.985
Je li ovo škola ili muzej?

00:17:09.153 --> 00:17:11.446
Još jedan. I poslednji.

00:17:11.614 --> 00:17:12.948
Tako.

00:17:14.117 --> 00:17:15.117
